{"tid":809120,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯有得簽中堅啦　寸王搵泰利幫拖","createTime":"2018-09-07T02:17:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T07:32:07.000Z","uid":161311,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"aacdd2d90aeb282052e1c129ddbab9b8c334649e","tid":809120,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T02:17:28.000Z","msg":"曼聯今夏轉會窗想收購中堅，但處處碰壁，空手而回，估唔到轉會窗關閉之後，反而可能有收獲。根據外媒爆料，曼聯領隊莫連奴打算簽入昔日車路士愛將泰利幫手頂住防線。 <br />\n<br />\n雖然轉會窗已經關閉，但球會仍然可以簽入自由身球員，37歲嘅泰利5月離開阿士東維拉之後，仍然未有班落，隨時可以成魔，據悉，曼聯已經派人聯絡佢。 <br />\n<br />\n曼聯今季4場聯賽已經失咗7球，表現認真曳，或者大家會覺得泰利已經一把年齡，恐怕應付唔到英超比賽節奏，但佢勝在經驗豐富，而且同莫連奴曾於車路士合作多年，清楚寸王嘅戰術要求，可以迅速融入球隊，或者真係可以穩住曼聯防線。"},{"pid":"a6325b4f405e96028c7fd13d22ff3468cc9436ff","tid":809120,"uid":158499,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T02:19:27.000Z","msg":"做後防教練會好啲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa3caaabdc8da28b51d1b827e352d2dfb523d4d","tid":809120,"uid":3514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T02:21:14.000Z","msg":"泰利個陣係咪有份迫鳩摩佬走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c537ca9ccc0d032e7b2d5a200a3cfa03a8faa23","tid":809120,"uid":42246,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"bfa3caaabdc8da28b51d1b827e352d2dfb523d4d","tid":809120,"uid":3514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T02:21:14.000Z","msg":"泰利個陣係咪有份迫鳩摩佬走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T02:23:40.000Z","msg":"冇啦 早幾個星期 泰利係ig玩你問我答<br />\n有條友問 佢跟個最好既教練係？<br />\n泰利答daddy"},{"pid":"0e228227be00f4899434a122d7236ca2cdc07700","tid":809120,"uid":124020,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T02:25:10.000Z","msg":"獌狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/sm